data.description: Perfection awaits! Don't miss this updated ranch home in the highly sought after Heard County! New Roof! Newer Carpet and Paint! Beautiful wooded 4 acres lot with a winding creek in your back yard! Come spend your hot summer days in the very large creek that stays kept year round! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style home has a spacious kitchen, a rock fireplace in the living room and a big back deck for family get togethers. With over 1800 square feet you have plenty of room to stretch out! Kitchen has an open concept with a formal dinning area and breakfast area! Well maintained hardwood floors in the living room area and leading down the hallway to your spacious bedrooms! Call or text for additional details! 678-378-7519
